    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to get this beauty into the hands of a new owner who will love it as much as I have. Honestly, it's been my pride and joy\u2014always garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and it still has that brand-new feel every time you get behind the wheel. It's in truly stunning shape, inside and out! I'm looking for a smooth, easy sale, so I've priced it to be a total steal for the condition it's in. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
