      "description": "This E46 M3 is a benchmark specimen of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L atmospheric straight-six delivers linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a recalibrated Double VANOS system, ensuring optimal cam phasing. This example features a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed cooling system with a high-flow water pump. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with the factory Variable M Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, and the paint depth remains consistent across all panels. Compression and leak-down results are within 2% of factory delivery specs, confirming the mechanical integrity of this collector-grade icon.",
